{"tid":633553,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]朋友好似考衰咗數學，點安慰佢好","createTime":"2018-04-18T12:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T13:40:06.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d47aa76735854d8ba1e7a14e69edfa92e177a1f5","tid":633553,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"我朋友份人不嬲幾有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPrep dse嗰陣都預自己會做得唔錯<br />\n話咩做mock出嚟都有粒星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己唔喺香港都唔知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係不嬲都冇聽講過佢讀書好，<br />\n唔係睇低佢中學差，我自己間中學都唔係好，我dse更加唔係好，依家上咗岸，我俾啲提議佢唔係好聽得入耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次講笑咁講 應間入咗ive就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就被佢屌:有邊日唔係食撚咗屎咁把口咁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到前幾日考完數學，全部人都屌哂老母話難，佢就灰哂，依幾日又覺都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話咩求4算 ，等價交換 求phy4換數學5<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只怕應間兩頭唔到岸 我frd諗埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己真係唔識安慰人，人又唔喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴絲教下小弟點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad80181d04fbbec06a8d77558d5c3e5a6b00786","tid":633553,"uid":176309,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"下年再黎過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961c4398c80becddbfc8c2c525acbb2142a488e3","tid":633553,"uid":76098,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"郵寄本數學past paper比佢 話下年比心基"},{"pid":"33ef80f6238238202e770a476130ecff5e647137","tid":633553,"uid":154746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"rep